### Youyu - Product & Shop Reviews
### Prerequisite: backend started with -Dspring-boot.run.profiles=seed

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userToken = mock-1001-USER
@adminToken = mock-9001-ADMIN

# ──────────────────── Product Reviews ────────────────────

### Submit product review (requires completed order — run order flow first)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/products
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderItemId": 1,
  "score": 5,
  "content": "Excellent quality, exactly as described."
}

### Submit product review - expect 401 (no token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderItemId": 1,
  "score": 4
}

### Submit product review - expect BAD_REQUEST (invalid score)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/products
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderItemId": 1,
  "score": 0
}

# ──────────────────── Shop Reviews ────────────────────

### Submit shop review (requires completed order from that shop)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/shops
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shopId": 4001,
  "score": 4,
  "content": "Good shop, fast shipping."
}

### Submit shop review - expect BUSINESS_ERROR (no completed order from shop)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/shops
Authorization: Bearer mock-1007-USER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shopId": 4001,
  "score": 3
}

# ──────────────────── Pending & My Reviews ────────────────────

### Get pending review items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Get my reviews (both product and shop)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

# ──────────────────── Public Endpoints ────────────────────

### Public: product review list (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/3002/reviews?page=1&pageSize=10

### Public: product review summary (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/3002/review-summary

### Public: shop review list (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shops/4001/reviews?page=1&pageSize=10

### Public: shop review summary (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shops/4001/review-summary
